---
title: Walnut & Rosemary-Crusted Chicken with Roasted Veggies & Garlic Aioli
description: What’s not to like about crusted chicken breast? It’s a great way to introduce texture and keep the chicken moist while it cooks.
The walnut and rosemary in the crust adds some amazing flavour, too!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/walnut-rosemary-crumbed-chicken-dc21fcf7.jpg
